summary:
In this time of YouTube toxicity, remember that not all YouTubers are bad or have bad messages! 
Sean McLoughlin: Positive...
body:
In this time of YouTube toxicity, remember that not all YouTubers are bad or have bad messages!

Sean McLoughlin: Positive mental attitude! Take time for self care, and LAUGH!

Arin Hanson: You can run a company with compassion and care about every employee, from cohost to intern.

Dan Avidan: Love everyone, forgive everyone, especially yourself. Dream big and work hard, and you can do anything!

Jenna Marbles: People will want to watch the content you love creating.
